normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，又相信旗下藝人，放手比佢地做自己鍾意嘅音樂，而且嗰啲音樂通常唔係最賺錢，但都依然肯投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85cf7bf992fa93ccf42f7d9677f77f950048ebc9","tid":627462,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:27:28.000Z","msg":"講到咁白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fe412f83929ec7c893b2cab18984dd2b9bb2f8","tid":627462,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:29:29.000Z","msg":"難得<br />\n香港真係太多偽人"},{"pid":"b4fc4c85f9929e61ec3cf342432f61bd7c84159a","tid":627462,"uid":124268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"有果句講果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b4857dfdfdd63a14a09083462a491f8c10add3","tid":627462,"uid":103339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"雖然機會好微，但如果佢攞獎上到台真心想聽佢會講咩"},{"pid":"abca1f754f2c679f40ff02adccca218e43a8e65a","tid":627462,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"好快d建制議員、林鄭又要聯署譴責杜汶澤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}